title: Care Bears - Land of Enchantment - DVDRip
description:
The Forest of Misfortune - Professor Coldheart and Frostbite plant a fortune-telling machine in the Forest of Feelings to fool Good Luck Bear.


Concrete Rain - Professor Coldheart invents an airborne cement mixer and plans to turn the world into a cold, hard, parking lot.

Runaway - Despite the Care Bears' warning.  Cara runs away when her parents try to get her to do something she dislikes.

Runtime 35 Minutes
